Pi0 analysis - Monte-Carlo simulation

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is a part of pi0 analysis code.
See StPi0Common/README for details.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

This directory contains macros and shell scripts needed to produce the 
Monte-Carlo simulated data.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
FILES

run_simulation
Shell script for the batch jobs to run starsim and BFC.

run_simulation.xml
The job description file for the scheduler.

submit.starsim.*
Job descriptions for the StPi0Common/macros/submit program.
In order to simulate the new particle, or with the new configuration, 
another submit.starsim.???? needs to be created.

*.kumac
The scripts for GEANT.
